name: Universe #240
description: Universe #240 - The seas filled with life on the worlds of Merus was calm for aeons. The tides turned suddenly with the apperance of 240. The seas started moving non-stop, pulling the ground below to the surface. The whole universe was in the brink of explosing when 240, despite being the cause, embraced Merus and prevented the explosion of the whole universe. Now the rubble swims on the face of 240 as the seas are once again calmed and peaceful on the core.
